---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Cta from '../components/Cta.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Travelope Premium Consultancy">
  <!-- Inner Page Hero -->
  <div class="relative pt-40 pb-20 overflow-hidden bg-[#0a2540]">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:40px_40px]"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-[#0a2540]/80 to-slate-50"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center">
      <span class="inline-block py-1.5 px-4 rounded-full bg-white/10 text-white font-bold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 shadow-sm border border-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white tracking-tight mb-6 drop-shadow-lg">Privacy <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#f97316] to-[#fdba74]">Policy</span></h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-200 font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed drop-shadow-md">Your Privacy Matters. We are certified by the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO).</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-24 bg-slate-50 text-slate-600 text-lg">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16">
        
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 font-medium mb-12 leading-relaxed">
          This Privacy Policy governs how Travelope ("we," "us," or "our") collects, processes, utilizes, and protects your personal information when you access our website or engage our visa consultation services. By accessing our services, you acknowledge and consent to the information practices described in this policy.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0a2540] mt-12 mb-6">Interpretation & Definitions</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-base">Capitalized terms used throughout this policy have specific meanings as defined below:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-base list-disc pl-5 mb-12">
          <li><strong>Account:</strong> A unique user profile established to facilitate access to our services</li>
          <li><strong>Company:</strong> Travelope, the data controller for the purposes of this policy</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Small data files stored on your computing device that retain browsing preferences and activity</li>
          <li><strong>Country:</strong> The United Kingdom, our primary jurisdiction of operation</li>
          <li><strong>Device:</strong> Any internet-capable equipment including smartphones, tablets, computers, or similar technology</li>
          <li><strong>Personal Data:</strong> Any information relating to an identified or identifiable natural person</li>
          <li><strong>Service:</strong> Our comprehensive visa consultation and application assistance services</li>
          <li><strong>Service Provider:</strong> Third-party organizations that process data on our behalf under contractual arrangements</li>
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information automatically collected regarding your interaction with our services</li>
          <li><strong>Website:</strong> Our online platform</li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="my-12 border-slate-200" />

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0a2540] mb-6 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 shadow-sm border border-blue-200"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" /></svg></span>
              Primary Personal Information
            </h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-base list-disc pl-5">
              <li>Complete legal name as appears on official documentation</li>
              <li>Primary and alternative email addresses</li>
              <li>Contact telephone numbers</li>
              <li>Passport and other government-issued identification details</li>
              <li>Nationality, citizenship status, and international travel history</li>
              <li>Financial and billing information for payment processing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0a2540] mb-6 flex items-center">
              <span class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 shadow-sm border border-purple-200"><svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg></span>
              Usage and Technical Data
            </h2>
            <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
              Usage Data is automatically generated during your interaction with our services. This encompasses your device's IP address, browser type and version, pages accessed, session duration, unique device identifiers, and additional diagnostic information. For mobile device users, we may additionally collect device model specifications and operating system versions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="my-12 border-slate-200" />

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0a2540] mt-12 mb-6">Tracking Technologies and Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-base">We employ cookies and similar tracking mechanisms to enhance user experience, analyze service utilization, and optimize website functionality.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0a2540] mb-2">Strictly Necessary Cookies</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Enable fundamental website operations and secure authentication processes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0a2540] mb-2">Functional Cookies</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Preserve user preferences and customization settings.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0a2540] mb-2">Performance Cookies</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Generate analytics data to assess website usage patterns and optimize performance.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#0a2540] mb-2">Targeting Cookies</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Monitor user engagement for marketing and advertising optimization.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0a2540] mt-12 mb-6">Purposes for Data Processing</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-base list-disc pl-5 mb-12">
          <li>Facilitating visa application preparation and submission procedures</li>
          <li>Maintaining communication regarding service requests and updates</li>
          <li>Processing payments and generating financial documentation</li>
          <li>Enhancing website functionality and service quality</li>
          <li>Ensuring compliance with legal and regulatory requirements</li>
          <li>Implementing fraud prevention and security measures</li>
          <li>Providing customer support and resolving inquiries</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0a2540] mt-12 mb-6">Data Sharing and International Transfers</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
          <p class="text-base"><strong class="text-[#0a2540]">Third-Party Processing:</strong> Your information may be processed at Travelope facilities or by authorized partners globally. Data transfers outside your jurisdiction are conducted with appropriate safeguards and security protocols.</p>
          <p class="text-base"><strong class="text-[#0a2540]">Corporate Transactions:</strong> In the event of merger, acquisition, or asset transfer, your Personal Data may be transferred to the acquiring entity. We will provide advance notification before your data becomes subject to alternative privacy policies.</p>
          <p class="text-base"><strong class="text-[#0a2540]">Legal Disclosure:</strong> We may disclose personal information when legally required or when necessary to protect our rights, property, or user safety, or to comply with judicial proceedings, court orders, or legal processes.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0a2540] mt-12 mb-6">Security & Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-base mb-4"><strong class="text-[#0a2540]">Data Security:</strong> We implement industry-standard security protocols to protect your personal information. However, no method of electronic transmission or storage can guarantee absolute security, and we cannot ensure complete protection against all potential security breaches.</p>
        <p class="text-base mb-4"><strong class="text-[#0a2540]">Minors' Privacy:</strong> Our services are not designed for or directed toward individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>
        <p class="text-base mb-12"><strong class="text-[#0a2540]">Data Retention:</strong> We retain personal data only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy or as required by applicable law.</p>

        <div class="bg-[#f97316]/10 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-[#f97316]/20 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0a2540] mb-2">Have Questions?</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">For questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us:</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="mailto:info@travelope.uk" class="font-bold text-[#f97316] hover:text-[#0a2540] transition-colors">info@travelope.uk</a>
            <span class="hidden sm:inline text-slate-300">|</span>
            <a href="tel:+447727748251" class="font-bold text-[#f97316] hover:text-[#0a2540] transition-colors">+44 7727748251</a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Cta />
</Layout>
